                <h3 class="card-title">DOWNLOAD SAR FILE TO DESKTOP</h3>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                <div class="paragraph" style="text-align:left;">
                  <span>Use any SCP software like Winscp/Filezilla/pscp/psftp to download the file from the server. Many prefer to use&nbsp;<a href="http://www.chiark.greenend.org.uk/~sgtatham/putty/download.html" style="color:pink">pscp</a> command to download the files from Unix server to the desktop.</span><br><br>
                  <div class="code-block"> pscp userid@hostname:/tmp/sa<span class="tdate"></span>_hostname.txt .</div><br><br><br></div>
              </div>
            </div>  
          </div>
